channel.title: Ultimate Study Guide - How to get good marks!
channel.description:
Theres alot of topics like: "Im going to fail!" and "I dont know how to Study!" So Im making this. It basicly tells you how to study well.
Well if your going to do well you need to study. There no way in hell you can do well without studying. You can maybe year 8 or 9 if you pay alot of attention in class (which just isn't fun). But the best way is to study and you must do it properly to get a decent mark. It may take sometime so hang in there.
The things you should do to study well.
[ul][li]Take Notes in class. This is not compulsary but is recomended. I only do this for important things.[/li] [li]Always ask your teacher if you dont understand something. Even if they are scarey :P.[/li] [li]When studying read through your textbook and write it all down. Make shit loads of notes. Not fun but this is very important.[/li] [li]STAY FOCUSED! Its a must dont take breaks for anything. Let nothing distract you from studying.[/li] [li]Take all your notes to the period before you test. Read them them all. DONT SKIM READ! Make sure you understand EVERYTHING.[/li][/ul]
Best Sites for Assignments: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page http://www.google.com
You obviously need to actually want to do well. Well you may not care now it WILL affect you job you get. You dont want to be some low class Labourer and having to slave your ass off for the rest of your working life.
Happy Studying Bitches :).
